One should not go with the fashions of the day,

00:23:14.389 --> 00:23:17.222
and take to something which is nonsensical,

00:23:17.806 --> 00:23:21.848
which is not good for your appearance,

00:23:22.222 --> 00:23:26.138
which makes you look funny or very fashionable

00:23:26.139 --> 00:23:27.931
like a dandy person.

00:23:28.347 --> 00:23:33.722
We have to wear a dress which is in the centre, dignified, which is good.

00:23:39.722 --> 00:23:44.806
Now I'm told that it is very difficult even to wake up in England.

00:23:45.472 --> 00:23:47.889
Somebody had told me, when I was young,

00:23:48.264 --> 00:23:50.597
that don't wake up an Englishman.

00:23:52.681 --> 00:23:56.430
I haven't tried that, even with a barge pole.

00:23:57.180 --> 00:24:00.681
I just tell you at this time, never in the morning time.

00:24:01.098 --> 00:24:03.931
Because I've been warned: never wake up an Englishman,

00:24:03.931 --> 00:24:06.222
that is the greatest sin on this earth!

00:24:12.764 --> 00:24:16.472
So why should the English be so much addicted to sleep!

00:24:17.139 --> 00:24:20.014
The whole country is sleeping today.

00:24:20.556 --> 00:24:24.430
They want more wages, more wages so that they can sleep more.

00:24:26.264 --> 00:24:30.180
Eat and drink, drink and eat in between, sleep.

00:24:30.222 --> 00:24:35.597
This is the three - programmed life.

00:24:38.472 --> 00:24:42.222
It was very difficult, from the very beginnig

00:24:42.264 --> 00:24:47.430
I saw Sahaja Yogis coming, in that to wake them up was difficult.

00:24:47.472 --> 00:24:53.222
And these are the same people who were known for punctuality

00:24:53.264 --> 00:24:57.931
that they won the war at Waterloo because of punctuality,

00:24:58.681 --> 00:25:04.098
and they were so punctual that people used to set their watches --

00:25:04.138 --> 00:25:06.931
even in America. They are the same people.

00:25:07.472 --> 00:25:11.931
Now the other side of it is that they sleep like log of wood.

00:25:12.389 --> 00:25:15.098
They used to sleep before also must be, because this is an old saying that.

00:25:15.138 --> 00:25:16.889
Don't wake up an Englishman.

00:25:17.681 --> 00:25:21.931
But I used to think something else about it why it is said,

00:25:21.931 --> 00:25:24.681
but it is nothing but simple laziness.

00:25:26.139 --> 00:25:33.056
So try to see why we sleep so much.

00:25:36.973 --> 00:25:41.098
If the left side is strong, people sleep.

00:25:42.014 --> 00:25:46.305
If the back Agnya is strong, people sleep.

00:25:46.472 --> 00:25:52.806
If the front Agnya is working too much

00:25:53.347 --> 00:25:55.722
then people don't sleep.

00:25:58.347 --> 00:26:01.347
So even if I say, "Don't sleep",

00:26:01.681 --> 00:26:06.973
it mean that you put your right Agnya in working condition,

00:26:06.973 --> 00:26:08.973
that means you start thinking.

00:26:09.014 --> 00:26:10.764
Which is against Sahaja Yoga again.

00:26:12.014 --> 00:26:14.973
So it would be left agnya, right agnya, right agnya, left agnya,

00:26:14.973 --> 00:26:16.264
left agnya, left agnya, right agnya, left agnya...

00:26:16.264 --> 00:26:18.514
It will be going from one to another.

00:26:20.597 --> 00:26:29.472
So in the centre you have to be with Christ.

00:26:33.138 --> 00:26:38.138
He is alert every second of the day;

00:26:43.931 --> 00:26:47.222
killing; beating, hitting,

00:26:48.472 --> 00:26:54.806
curing, looking after, guiding.

00:26:55.597 --> 00:27:04.681
Twenty four hours a day. And go and ask any realized soul

00:27:04.722 --> 00:27:07.389
who is called as Avadhuta, the one who is a master,

00:27:07.430 --> 00:27:11.722
they will tell you they hardly sleep for three hours or four hours.

00:27:12.389 --> 00:27:15.889
Because they cannot work when they are sleeping,

00:27:16.138 --> 00:27:17.639
so they sleep for four hours,

00:27:17.681 --> 00:27:19.556
the rest of the time they are working:

00:27:20.264 --> 00:27:24.556
either they meditate and do things by projection,

00:27:25.098 --> 00:27:28.389
or they work with their hands.

00:27:28.973 --> 00:27:31.722
They are busy people, they are very busy.

00:27:32.222 --> 00:27:39.639
You have to be very busy people because now you are employed by God.

00:27:40.138 --> 00:27:45.514
And you have to do full justice to this employment by working hard.

00:27:46.138 --> 00:27:52.389
On the contrary you have seen that it is very easy to get lazy.

00:27:58.180 --> 00:28:02.973
So now, as many of you are already feeling sleepy, put your....

00:28:03.806 --> 00:28:07.138
First thing should be for all those people who are lazy,

00:28:07.138 --> 00:28:09.931
is to put their right to the left seven times -

00:28:10.014 --> 00:28:11.305
let's have it.

00:28:14.098 --> 00:28:16.514
With the right hand....

00:28:31.931 --> 00:28:37.138
It's better? Now the back Agnya.

00:28:37.138 --> 00:28:39.014
Let's have it.

00:28:41.931 --> 00:28:48.889
Laziness is first. Shri Krishna was against laziness.

00:28:48.889 --> 00:28:53.973
Anywhere he got a chance he talked against laziness, Alasya.

00:28:55.931 --> 00:28:57.848
Now watch me.

00:28:58.764 --> 00:29:00.889
On the photograph you can do the same....

00:29:58.889 --> 00:30:00.556
Better now?

00:30:04.430 --> 00:30:08.138
Tonight we have to keep awake; it's a big problem.

00:30:09.848 --> 00:30:12.764
But don't sleep formally here. Alright ?

00:30:12.889 --> 00:30:14.806
Informally you can.

00:30:28.889 --> 00:30:30.806
Better ?

00:30:33.014 --> 00:30:36.597
Put your eyes, try Again.

00:31:08.848 --> 00:31:12.973
So the mastery should be, first of all, of your body.

00:31:14.806 --> 00:31:17.681
Say, you are sleeping on one side, you get a pain --

00:31:17.681 --> 00:31:19.889
then what do you do? You sleep on the other side.

00:31:21.681 --> 00:31:25.764
In the same way, this body is to be made

00:31:25.764 --> 00:31:29.472
immune to different shocks,

00:31:29.514 --> 00:31:32.806
you see. Like you put the watch in the water.

00:31:33.264 --> 00:31:36.597
You shock it with the water, so it is waterproof.

00:31:37.056 --> 00:31:40.305
So a Sahaja Yogi has to be an all-proofed person.

00:31:41.973 --> 00:31:50.889
So he has no place to complain,

00:31:51.597 --> 00:31:54.014
because he's supposed to be all-proof, you see.

00:31:54.056 --> 00:31:57.098
Anybody (Sahaja Yogi) who complains, you can say,

00:31:57.138 --> 00:31:58.931
"How are you complaining?

00:31:58.931 --> 00:32:00.514
Because you have to be all-proof."

00:32:02.305 --> 00:32:12.098
So no complaints of any kind, of Sahaja Yogis

00:32:12.138 --> 00:32:14.514
are to be accepted or sympathized.

00:32:20.180 --> 00:32:25.430
If you start accepting people who are complaining type

00:32:26.014 --> 00:32:28.347
you will be always busy looking after them,

00:32:28.848 --> 00:32:32.389
and you will be of no use to Sahaja Yoga.

00:32:34.138 --> 00:32:37.931
Those who have habits of complaininig and all that

00:32:37.973 --> 00:32:40.056
should go to the hospital and stay there.

00:32:40.681 --> 00:32:44.347
Complaining people are really people

00:32:44.389 --> 00:32:47.222
who have some sort of possession,

00:32:47.264 --> 00:32:51.305
I think, that they all the time complain and try to torture you,

00:32:51.848 --> 00:32:54.138
and make a nuisance out of themselves.

00:32:54.848 --> 00:32:57.138
Such people cannot become Gurus.

00:32:57.138 --> 00:33:01.973
Imagine - if the Guru is complaining then what is he going to teach?

00:33:02.014 --> 00:33:03.806
Only complaining.

00:33:04.556 --> 00:33:07.639
The teachers will be expert in complaining

00:33:07.639 --> 00:33:09.889
and the students will be also experts in complaining.

00:33:10.222 --> 00:33:15.056
So you create a set of complaining disciples, you see,

00:33:16.347 --> 00:33:18.472
And when they come to Me what I find

00:33:18.514 --> 00:33:22.264
they all have double lists than yourselves about their complaints.

00:33:24.139 --> 00:33:26.556
But also it is very characteristic.

00:33:26.597 --> 00:33:28.806
Like Australians seldom complain,

00:33:29.430 --> 00:33:32.098
and if they do complain they are hit also very badly.

00:33:32.639 --> 00:33:35.722
Seldom you will find an Australian complaining.

00:33:35.722 --> 00:33:37.889
I have got letters - except one or two

00:33:38.305 --> 00:33:41.222
who have now found themselves out - seldom

00:33:41.889 --> 00:33:46.222
they complain about themselves, about their body comforts,

00:33:46.222 --> 00:33:49.389
this thing that thing. So under any circumstances

00:33:49.931 --> 00:33:54.722
those who can live are the people

00:33:55.139 --> 00:33:57.681
who have achieved the one sixteenth,

00:33:58.138 --> 00:33:59.722
only the one sixteenth.

00:33:59.973 --> 00:34:02.681
(Jaise rakhahu taise hi rahu)

00:34:02.681 --> 00:34:06.389
Mother the way you keep it we are willing to stay.

00:34:06.931 --> 00:34:09.931
Of course the Mother has kept you very well.

00:34:13.430 --> 00:34:16.180
All the luxuries of world Mother has given you.

00:34:17.764 --> 00:34:20.514
She doesn't torture you like other Gurus have tortured.

00:34:21.014 --> 00:34:22.764
Once and for all.

00:34:23.138 --> 00:34:25.973
My Son has gone through all the tortures,

00:34:27.180 --> 00:34:32.139
there is no need to put you to any tortures or troubles.

00:34:32.347 --> 00:34:34.597
But you should see how your body reacts,

00:34:34.639 --> 00:34:39.639
and tell your body, "Yes Mr body, will you please now,

00:34:39.639 --> 00:34:42.764
behave yourself and not try to be indulgent."

00:34:44.639 --> 00:34:51.056
All these indulgences come to us through our senses.

00:34:51.556 --> 00:34:54.848
So if you can master your body

00:34:54.848 --> 00:34:57.347
you will also master your senses.

00:34:57.889 --> 00:35:08.597
For example the master, or we say the highest of the organs

00:35:08.639 --> 00:35:12.180
which controls most of the organs, I personally think, is the tongue.

00:35:12.848 --> 00:35:17.347
Because it's the primordial nonsense.

00:35:20.597 --> 00:35:26.973
By tongue we speak things to hurt others.

00:35:27.597 --> 00:35:32.347
With tongue we learn how to go on jabbering.

00:35:32.931 --> 00:35:36.806
With tongue we can show how frivolous we are.

00:35:37.514 --> 00:35:40.722
Either we are tongue tied or tongue - loose,

00:35:41.014 --> 00:35:43.639
there's nothing in between with the tongue.

00:35:43.639 --> 00:35:46.056
That's only about talking part, that's lower.

00:35:46.472 --> 00:35:50.098
But when it comes higher, eating;

00:35:52.098 --> 00:35:54.138
all the time thinking about eating.

00:35:54.138 --> 00:35:57.722
I have told you a hundred times, that Sahaja Yogis should go

00:35:57.722 --> 00:36:03.222
on really sometimes on absolutely bland boiled horrible food --

00:36:04.639 --> 00:36:11.639
just to test the tongue. Do it, try this, then try this.

00:36:11.889 --> 00:36:15.806
My father used to tell that you must burn your tongue a little bit.

00:36:16.305 --> 00:36:18.848
That's one of the tests he said one should do.

00:36:18.848 --> 00:36:21.056
But he was a hard taskmaster as a Guru.

00:36:21.639 --> 00:36:24.722
So we should see what our tongue can bear,

00:36:25.305 --> 00:36:28.138
is it fussy about food ?

00:36:33.056 --> 00:36:38.222
When it sees the food does it start watering, first of all;

00:36:42.514 --> 00:36:45.430
does it take our attention to food,

00:36:46.014 --> 00:36:47.931
is food important to us?

00:36:48.430 --> 00:37:00.973
So the first thing, to overcome the problem of your tongue is

00:37:00.973 --> 00:37:05.722
"to starve." Starvation is the only way

00:37:05.764 --> 00:37:09.264
you can correct yourself. You see if you starve yourself --

00:37:09.347 --> 00:37:15.848
say, morning just have little to eat, reduce it to half.

00:37:15.889 --> 00:37:18.722
You'll be surprised your intestine will be halved also.

00:37:18.722 --> 00:37:21.639
After some time you cannot eat more even if you want to.

00:37:22.347 --> 00:37:26.639
Your interest will go off. Train up yourself.

00:37:26.681 --> 00:37:28.681
Starvation is a very good thing.

00:37:28.681 --> 00:37:32.180
I think 40 days that Christ did is a very good idea.

00:37:34.722 --> 00:37:39.722
But that should not be a kind of a thing that like - they have Ramazan,

00:37:40.098 --> 00:37:45.806
that they eat the most s..... food during that time early in the morning

00:37:45.806 --> 00:37:48.222
then the whole day they starve - thinking about food!

00:37:51.430 --> 00:37:57.514
Starve yourself fully and don't think about food.

00:37:57.514 --> 00:37:59.764
That's difficult so starve yourself  in halfway

00:38:00.138 --> 00:38:01.639
and dont think about food.

00:38:03.098 --> 00:38:05.848
Gradually try to master your tongue.

00:38:06.597 --> 00:38:10.180
Mastery of your tongue is only possible if you know

00:38:10.222 --> 00:38:13.389
how to starve your day. This is for the western side.

00:38:13.472 --> 00:38:17.430
For eastern side they fast morning till evening.

00:38:18.681 --> 00:38:21.056
I know one lady, if you ask them they say

00:38:21.098 --> 00:38:25.139
"I observe Monday, I observe Tuesday, I observe Wednesday,

00:38:25.180 --> 00:38:28.764
I observe Thursday, I observe Friday a fast,

00:38:28.806 --> 00:38:35.014
and perhaps maybe if I do not starve Saturday I will eat on Sunday."

00:38:35.848 --> 00:38:39.139
I have know such people in my life time - many --

00:38:39.681 --> 00:38:41.848
who just go on fasting.

00:38:41.848 --> 00:38:43.973
They are such experts and astute? you see,

00:38:44.597 --> 00:38:48.514
that they can show you that they can fast for 50 days, 80 days,

00:38:48.514 --> 00:38:52.556
108 days, and 300 days.

00:38:53.056 --> 00:38:55.139
Starving masters.

00:38:55.639 --> 00:38:59.389
So for them I have to tell, "you have to eat'', when they are starve.

00:38:59.430 --> 00:39:01.014
To you I have to say,

00:39:01.014 --> 00:39:04.681
"Let us see which day we can starve ourselves."

00:39:04.681 --> 00:39:11.138
Let us have one day to celebrate today's great day of Nanaka!

00:39:11.138 --> 00:39:14.806
One day let us starve. Which day should we?

00:39:17.056 --> 00:39:21.889
Monday we cannot because Monday we have a programme,

00:39:23.472 --> 00:39:29.056
Tuesday we cannot because it is a day when Hanuman has to work,

00:39:32.722 --> 00:39:35.764
Wednesday we cannot, because then the creativity takes place,

00:39:37.347 --> 00:39:40.639
Thursday we cannot because we are Guru at that day,

00:39:40.681 --> 00:39:43.889
we have to work very hard as Gurus, Friday we cannot,

00:39:43.931 --> 00:39:46.056
we have to work the shakti of Mother,

00:39:46.056 --> 00:39:48.556
Saturday we cannot because we have to do

00:39:48.556 --> 00:39:52.430
all the intrigue of Shri Krishna.

00:39:53.138 --> 00:39:56.347
And Sunday how can it be, this is the day of the sun!"

00:39:59.056 --> 00:40:03.138
So which is the best day for starving, now let us see.

00:40:04.305 --> 00:40:10.597
We should have Thursday, because Thursday is the Guru's day

00:40:10.931 --> 00:40:15.597
and let us do some fasting, half day, half day can we?

00:40:15.639 --> 00:40:18.848
Can we start with half day then f... day?

00:40:18.848 --> 00:40:21.848
Thursday let us have, maybe second half

00:40:21.848 --> 00:40:24.222
because breakfast is essential I think.

00:40:25.305 --> 00:40:28.556
Without breakfast you see, the horses cannot whinny,

00:40:31.222 --> 00:40:33.305
so let us have the second half

00:40:36.681 --> 00:40:39.056
or we can have the first half.

00:40:39.806 --> 00:40:45.430
Actually you have to discipline yourself, if you have to be the Gurus.

00:40:45.472 --> 00:40:48.222
It's like going to a college,

00:40:48.430 --> 00:40:50.264
when you are left to yourself,

00:40:50.305 --> 00:40:53.180
it is you, who has to discipline yourself,

00:40:53.222 --> 00:40:56.138
nobody has to tell you that you do this and do that

00:40:56.138 --> 00:40:58.347
That's the measure to wake you up.

00:40:58.389 --> 00:41:01.430
In India it is the other way around.

00:41:01.430 --> 00:41:04.764
If you tell somebody that you have to wake up at 5,

00:41:05.556 --> 00:41:10.806
the person who has told you will be awakened at 4 o' clock himself,

00:41:10.848 --> 00:41:15.139
the one who has told; so that he doesn't get up to wake him up.

00:41:15.889 --> 00:41:17.639
Did you follow me?

00:41:18.180 --> 00:41:20.889
And the whole house will be awakened at 4 o'clock

00:41:21.305 --> 00:41:24.264
so that they can take up the duty from the person

00:41:24.264 --> 00:41:25.764
who has to get awakened.

00:41:28.098 --> 00:41:29.889
But the fellow who has to awaken

00:41:29.931 --> 00:41:31.597
might not sleep the whole night.

00:41:32.556 --> 00:41:36.014
It is just the other way round, the other extreme of it.

00:41:36.430 --> 00:41:42.764
Say if I am there, one night I sleep there. If I get up

00:41:43.305 --> 00:41:46.514
at one o'clock I find all of them sitting and meditating,

00:41:46.514 --> 00:41:49.138
in the passage, up to the bathroom everywhere.

00:41:49.139 --> 00:41:52.180
They have not gone home, not taken food, nothing.

00:41:52.681 --> 00:41:55.222
Just meditating, taking vibrations, correcting.

00:41:55.222 --> 00:41:56.889
I am sleeping inside.

00:41:56.889 --> 00:41:59.138
In the night I want to go to the bathroom,

00:41:59.138 --> 00:42:01.264
I just cannot go because they are all meditating.

00:42:01.305 --> 00:42:03.472
Nobody is sleeping, nobody is sleeping.

00:42:09.889 --> 00:42:12.180
So it is the other way around.

00:42:13.138 --> 00:42:15.806
So to you people let us do one day.

00:42:15.806 --> 00:42:21.138
That you must have one day fasting, one day keeping, one awake.

00:42:21.681 --> 00:42:24.222
Which day should it be? Let's see.

00:42:27.222 --> 00:42:29.806
A day when there is no film!

00:42:37.597 --> 00:42:44.848
Half night, second half I mean, not the first half.

00:42:48.722 --> 00:43:00.139
Which day? Which is the most difficult day when you cannot,

00:43:02.138 --> 00:43:09.973
cannot keep awake. Sunday night;

00:43:10.973 --> 00:43:13.597
but there's a fiIm on!

00:43:16.305 --> 00:43:19.639
Without the film, you see!

00:43:19.639 --> 00:43:22.722
Treat yourself like that, joke with yourself,

00:43:22.722 --> 00:43:25.556
now Sunday night is there a film on?

00:43:25.597 --> 00:43:27.222
After 12 there isn't.

00:43:27.264 --> 00:43:29.597
So Sunday night you get up at 12 o'clock.

00:43:29.639 --> 00:43:36.931
Let's have it. Enjoy it. Don't get angry.

00:43:38.973 --> 00:43:41.098
Make a fun out of it.

00:43:43.973 --> 00:43:48.138
You think more about it, then you get upset.

00:43:48.139 --> 00:43:50.180
You just don't think about it, then you'll enjoy it.

00:43:50.180 --> 00:43:51.722
It's like swimming.

00:43:51.764 --> 00:43:56.264
Get up at 12 o'clock, all of you, go for a bath, sit down,

00:43:56.305 --> 00:43:59.973
sing Bhajans, this, that, let us do it. Should we ?

00:44:04.722 --> 00:44:07.681
Michel, What happen with you?

00:44:07.722 --> 00:44:14.180
"I can go to bed at two o clock"

00:44:14.180 --> 00:44:18.098
You have to get up at 12 o'clock,

00:44:18.098 --> 00:44:22.139
you have to go to bed till 12 o'clock.

00:44:22.180 --> 00:44:24.139
Get up at 12 o'clock.

00:44:24.180 --> 00:44:28.138
You see the first half of the night, one must sleep always, it's better.

00:44:28.347 --> 00:44:32.639
Second half of the night is the better part, alright?

00:44:32.848 --> 00:44:36.014
So the first half of the night you all have to sleep, anytime.

00:44:36.056 --> 00:44:39.139
You can sleep about 8 o'clock or 9 o'clock if you want to.

00:44:41.681 --> 00:44:44.889
But that should not be important, what time you sleep,

00:44:44.889 --> 00:44:48.014
you have to get up at 12 o'clock in the morning,

00:44:48.681 --> 00:44:50.848
or say after 12.

00:44:54.722 --> 00:44:57.806
Shri Krishna was born in the night about 12 o'clock.

00:44:57.806 --> 00:45:00.014
Nanaka was born 12 o'clock in the night.

00:45:00.014 --> 00:45:04.222
All the Gurus mostly took their birth at 12 o'clock in the night.

00:45:05.056 --> 00:45:10.681
To celebrate that, we must have one day when we do not sleep after 12.

00:45:11.347 --> 00:45:15.138
But then what about Caxton Hall!

00:45:15.597 --> 00:45:18.681
"Mother we can try this on Saturday.

00:45:18.764 --> 00:45:20.264
¿What?

00:45:20.764 --> 00:45:23.389
¿Can we do it in Saturday night? It will be more safe

00:45:23.722 --> 00:45:26.389
because will be less incidents the Sunday that Monday"

00:45:26.556 --> 00:45:34.056
Alright so you can sleep in the day time of Saturday or of Sunday.

00:45:34.514 --> 00:45:36.264
Sunday afternoon you can sleep.

00:45:36.347 --> 00:45:38.597
No, no, no that won't be alright.

00:45:41.430 --> 00:45:44.014
If you make any compensation

00:45:44.056 --> 00:45:46.722
then you are not torturing your body much!

00:45:48.639 --> 00:45:51.222
You must devise a method by which

00:45:51.264 --> 00:45:54.347
your body does see that it has to get up at 12 o'clock,

00:45:54.389 --> 00:45:55.764
Better keep it that time.

00:45:55.806 --> 00:45:58.138
What do you think ? Alright.

00:45:58.138 --> 00:46:02.347
"¿Do you think that this may affect the job on Monday?"

00:46:02.389 --> 00:46:04.430
¿What he said?

00:46:04.472 --> 00:46:06.639
"That the job of the people may be affected

00:46:06.639 --> 00:46:08.222
on Monday morning, Mother".

00:46:08.264 --> 00:46:13.681
They will never, take it from me, they will not:

00:46:13.681 --> 00:46:16.138
You see work is not important what is important

00:46:16.139 --> 00:46:21.639
is your Spirit, your mastery.

00:46:21.681 --> 00:46:25.180
Work, in any case you're not going to have after some time,

00:46:25.931 --> 00:46:28.180
so that work is not important.

00:46:28.222 --> 00:46:31.472
This new work that you have taken, better look after that.

00:46:31.472 --> 00:46:35.472
Forget about your work. Forget about these things.

00:46:35.514 --> 00:46:38.098
What is important is your Spirit.

00:46:38.138 --> 00:46:40.347
Otherwise you cannot become Gurus.

00:46:41.138 --> 00:46:43.138
Spirit is the most important thing.

00:46:43.139 --> 00:46:46.806
The rest of the things are absolutely unimportant,

00:46:46.806 --> 00:46:48.722
a zero.

00:46:51.556 --> 00:46:56.347
I've been very slowly trying to take you out

00:46:56.389 --> 00:47:00.806
of the mud of materialism and of these mundane things.

00:47:01.305 --> 00:47:06.430
But you have to work for God. You are special people.

00:47:07.973 --> 00:47:12.389
So, you have to make yourself a master,

00:47:14.098 --> 00:47:19.430
so God gives you all the blessings, everything.

00:47:20.430 --> 00:47:23.848
But the idea of luxurious life must be given up.

00:47:24.556 --> 00:47:28.056
People want to make this life luxurious,

00:47:28.931 --> 00:47:31.347
then you'll have the luxury of this world

00:47:31.389 --> 00:47:34.472
but not the luxury of God's blessings.

00:47:35.014 --> 00:47:37.098
One of the two you have to select.

00:47:37.556 --> 00:47:50.848
Either you lead a life which is luxurious on the material level,

00:47:50.973 --> 00:47:54.848
or you lead a luxurious life of God's blessings.

00:47:54.848 --> 00:47:57.722
One of the two you have to choose, the time has come.

00:47:58.180 --> 00:48:01.681
So nothing is important you see,

00:48:01.681 --> 00:48:05.056
the insecurity of money also is another nonsense.

00:48:05.056 --> 00:48:07.264
At least you people should not have it.

00:48:08.056 --> 00:48:10.681
I mean you will never starve at least,

00:48:10.722 --> 00:48:14.056
but Indians if they do not work they will starve.

00:48:16.389 --> 00:48:19.556
But you people can never starve, if you are unemployed,

00:48:19.556 --> 00:48:25.014
government is happy more, as long as you don't bother them.

00:48:25.889 --> 00:48:28.597
If you sit at home and meditate

00:48:28.639 --> 00:48:30.056
they'll be very happy.

00:48:31.098 --> 00:48:36.556
So to earn more money or to make more money

00:48:36.597 --> 00:48:38.764
is not important at all in Sahaja Yoga.

00:48:40.597 --> 00:48:43.681
Most important thing is to be the Spirit.

00:48:43.722 --> 00:48:45.931
For that whatever is to be done has to be done.

00:48:46.639 --> 00:48:52.430
Let everything suffer, you don't make your Spirit suffer.

00:48:55.014 --> 00:49:03.556
Because you have to become the full moon, like Guru Nanak.

00:49:04.222 --> 00:49:07.430
How much did Guru Nanak earn?

00:49:12.681 --> 00:49:19.973
You should find out, how did he live his life ?

00:49:25.764 --> 00:49:30.973
There is nothing to bother about money,

00:49:31.931 --> 00:49:35.014
because more money is not needed.

00:49:37.639 --> 00:49:42.138
Just needed for your food and your living.

00:49:43.639 --> 00:49:46.597
And then money is arranged if you need

00:49:46.597 --> 00:49:48.639
any extra money sometimes, emergencies.

00:49:48.681 --> 00:49:51.222
I've done it for many Australians, you know.

00:49:51.639 --> 00:49:55.681
But those are the people who have dedicated themselves fully.

00:49:57.848 --> 00:50:00.222
And that is why they have been helped,

00:50:00.264 --> 00:50:02.722
whenever there is an emergency they don't have to bother.

00:50:03.305 --> 00:50:08.180
But the dedication to your Spirit has to be full, complete,

00:50:08.806 --> 00:50:12.305
and nothing to your work, actually.

00:50:13.056 --> 00:50:15.722
Because that goes hand in hand.

00:50:16.556 --> 00:50:20.973
If you are not worried about yourself after realisation,

00:50:22.138 --> 00:50:26.222
about your Spirit, you'll have all the problems of the world.

00:50:26.806 --> 00:50:29.056
First and foremost is financial problems.

00:50:35.138 --> 00:50:44.138
Then, physical problem, mental problem, emotional problem.

00:50:44.806 --> 00:50:46.806
All kinds of problems will follow,

00:50:46.848 --> 00:50:50.848
because I've awakened your Kundalini; one part I've done.

00:50:51.806 --> 00:50:54.472
But another part that is your heart, you have not opened.

00:50:54.514 --> 00:50:56.806
You must give your heart to Sahaja Yoga.

00:50:57.347 --> 00:50:59.430
You have not opened your heart as yet.

00:51:00.139 --> 00:51:03.056
Heart has to be opened.

00:51:03.556 --> 00:51:06.014
You are still woried about your father, mother,

00:51:06.056 --> 00:51:07.889
brother, sister, wife, children.

00:51:08.597 --> 00:51:14.973
Open your heart fully to Sahaja Yoga.

00:51:15.556 --> 00:51:17.597
In a doubtless way.

00:51:18.139 --> 00:51:20.597
Then only doubt less awareness will settle down.

00:51:21.222 --> 00:51:23.973
Unless and until you open your heart,

00:51:24.139 --> 00:51:26.264
Kundalini rising has no meaning.

00:51:26.848 --> 00:51:31.347
Because the Kundalini is rising but the heart has not opened.

00:51:31.973 --> 00:51:36.056
If the Mother Earth sends forth her power through the seed

00:51:36.056 --> 00:51:39.138
and the seed doesn't open, then what's the use ?

00:51:39.138 --> 00:51:40.889
It's all a myth.

00:51:40.931 --> 00:51:43.138
Open your heart to Sahaja Yoga.

00:51:43.347 --> 00:51:46.056
Open your heart to Spirit, and say,

00:51:46.056 --> 00:51:48.014
"Mother we are the Spirit."

00:51:50.056 --> 00:51:51.639
You have to realize this,

00:51:51.681 --> 00:51:53.722
many people also perhaps do no realize

00:51:53.722 --> 00:51:57.514
that you have come on this earth to be the Spirit

00:51:57.973 --> 00:52:00.806
and not to be workers of human beings.

00:52:02.556 --> 00:52:08.347
You must understand your greatness and know

00:52:08.389 --> 00:52:12.389
that you are not like mundan people. That's why you are blessed.

00:52:13.014 --> 00:52:14.681
Who is blessed so much ?

00:52:15.264 --> 00:52:18.056
You are described long time back by Blake,

00:52:18.556 --> 00:52:21.347
that such and such people are going to come on this earth

00:52:21.389 --> 00:52:23.764
"men of God." Men of God.

00:52:25.305 --> 00:52:28.681
What do you have in your heart?

00:52:30.556 --> 00:52:33.931
Your heart will be like a stone.

00:52:34.430 --> 00:52:37.389
Unless and until there is light of the Spirit

00:52:37.389 --> 00:52:39.806
it is a stone heart,

00:52:39.848 --> 00:52:47.764
and this stone is going to hurt everyone, is going to ruin you completely.

00:52:48.222 --> 00:52:52.305
Open your heart hundred percent.

00:52:57.514 --> 00:52:59.973
You have met Indian Sahaja Yogis,

00:53:01.098 --> 00:53:02.681
they have problems of money.

00:53:03.681 --> 00:53:06.639
And how much they work for Sahaja Yoga,

00:53:07.098 --> 00:53:12.764
day in and day out how much they have contributed for Sahaja Yoga.

00:53:13.305 --> 00:53:18.138
You can imagine, about 7 lakhs of rupees they have collected,

00:53:18.138 --> 00:53:25.597
Rustom knows. 7 lakhs of rupees, they have collected for their ashram.

00:53:26.139 --> 00:53:35.264
7 lakhs is about £35000.£ 35000 they have collected only in Bombay.

00:53:35.556 --> 00:53:39.931
In Delhi they have collected about 5 lakhs, £ 25000.

00:53:42.848 --> 00:53:45.681
They are working, they have families they have children,

00:53:46.222 --> 00:53:49.806
but what they think about is nothing but Sahaja Yoga,

00:53:49.806 --> 00:53:51.848
nothing but Sahaja Yoga, nothing but Sahaja Yoga.

00:53:58.098 --> 00:54:01.722
They give most of their money for Sahaja Yoga, I think.

00:54:02.556 --> 00:54:04.305
They live with minimum.

00:54:04.848 --> 00:54:09.056
If I tell them why don't you buy another shirt for yourself,

00:54:09.722 --> 00:54:15.514
they will say, "Mother, I have worn lots of shirts in my previous life,"

00:54:18.138 --> 00:54:21.889
So satisfied ! "We have found the Atma now,

00:54:21.931 --> 00:54:24.264
let us dress up the Atma.

00:54:24.305 --> 00:54:28.430
We have found out our heart, let us become the heart".

00:54:28.472 --> 00:54:30.889
What is the need to worry about these things ?

00:54:30.931 --> 00:54:33.180
We have done enough of all this nonsense.

00:54:33.973 --> 00:54:38.430
I tell you they will think they are poor, but they are not.

00:54:39.848 --> 00:54:42.722
Wherever they can save their money they will save it.

00:54:43.222 --> 00:54:45.722
They used to give me some money before, I said,

00:54:45.764 --> 00:54:47.889
"No I don't need just now, there's no need"

00:54:47.889 --> 00:54:49.806
They said I have no place to keep;

00:54:49.848 --> 00:54:51.973
there is no trust, nothing, how are we to do it?

00:54:52.514 --> 00:55:02.472
They continued like this till about, I think, in, 74,

00:55:06.764 --> 00:55:10.222
when I went back we thought of starting an ashram,

00:55:10.264 --> 00:55:12.806
because you people were all coming there.

00:55:14.848 --> 00:55:20.556
So I said alright, now you have to give me money,

00:55:20.597 --> 00:55:23.722
all the Sahaja Yogis can give me money, whatever they have saved.

00:55:24.222 --> 00:55:27.264
And you'll be amazed everyone came out with 1000 rupees,

00:55:27.305 --> 00:55:32.472
every one of them, whether he was a labourer or every one of them,

00:55:32.514 --> 00:55:37.014
1000 rupees minimum. Up to 21 000.

00:55:37.764 --> 00:55:40.973
In 3 years time they had saved,

00:55:41.014 --> 00:55:42.889
because they thought it is our responsibility

00:55:42.931 --> 00:55:44.514
to save money for Sahaja Yoga.

00:55:44.556 --> 00:55:46.931
Tomorrow if we have to have an ashram how are we going to have ?

00:55:52.138 --> 00:55:54.889
But we still indulge into things.

00:56:02.681 --> 00:56:07.014
So this is what is the Gurupada.

00:56:07.056 --> 00:56:12.931
This Sir has to sit down, make an space for him.

00:56:12.973 --> 00:56:16.514
Come on, please. He doesn't need to be stand up. All right.

00:56:20.639 --> 00:56:24.305
So today is such a great day of Guru Nanaka's birthday,

00:56:25.264 --> 00:56:29.430
and we have to see his own life, how he spent his own life,

00:56:29.764 --> 00:56:35.931
how he lived and in what conditions he managed.

00:56:38.138 --> 00:56:42.973
So the first thing is to look after, disciplining yourself,

00:56:43.556 --> 00:56:47.222
feeling responsible for Sahaja Yoga.

00:56:48.056 --> 00:56:52.014
I was amazed people told, me that in the ashram

00:56:52.056 --> 00:56:57.138
people keep the lights on, and the oil costs so much,

00:56:57.139 --> 00:57:02.098
300 pounds every week. I'm amazed!

00:57:03.389 --> 00:57:07.639
Every one of you should be responsi-be for every electricity,

00:57:07.639 --> 00:57:11.347
everything that you spend here. This is God's place.

00:57:15.098 --> 00:57:19.264
Somebody has given the car, everybody wants to use the car.

00:57:19.305 --> 00:57:21.597
You see this saving the pounds

00:57:21.639 --> 00:57:24.056
is still going on the heads of Sahaja Yogis.

00:57:24.889 --> 00:57:28.056
If they can save by taking somebody's car they would borrow.

00:57:28.098 --> 00:57:29.514
Never borrow anybody's car.

00:57:29.514 --> 00:57:31.889
It's not for you, you must have your self respect,

00:57:31.889 --> 00:57:33.556
why to borrow anybody's car?

00:57:33.556 --> 00:57:35.931
It's not to be done.

00:57:39.138 --> 00:57:42.973
So the second point of the Self is self respect.

00:57:43.556 --> 00:57:46.722
First is the respect of your body,

00:57:47.264 --> 00:57:49.806
and the second is self-respect.

00:57:53.556 --> 00:57:57.764
We are arrogant, we can be rude,

00:57:59.597 --> 00:58:01.430
but we have no self respect.

00:58:10.556 --> 00:58:13.722
But it is the training that is lacking,

00:58:14.389 --> 00:58:16.722
you see suddenly I find after war

00:58:16.722 --> 00:58:22.931
there has been no teaching how to be self respecting.

00:58:25.138 --> 00:58:30.347
Like in the war, might be, the atmosphere might have been created I don't know why - that-

00:58:30.347 --> 00:58:33.056
"I´m above everything, don't care for others."

00:58:35.973 --> 00:58:39.138
May have been; I don't know why this kind of a thing has come,

00:58:39.138 --> 00:58:41.264
but it is so. Very prevalent.

00:58:41.305 --> 00:58:43.722
But you people have to be other way round:

00:58:44.222 --> 00:58:47.639
'Others are first and then yourself.

00:58:47.639 --> 00:58:49.264
With your self respect.

00:58:49.264 --> 00:58:52.597
Doesn't matter, nobody is going to die, I can tell you this much.

00:58:59.347 --> 00:59:04.305
You all must have self respect; and such mediocre people

00:59:04.764 --> 00:59:07.430
should not be allowed to stay in Sahaja Yoga,

00:59:10.138 --> 00:59:15.264
at least in the ashram, because it brings a bad name to all Sahaja Yoga.

00:59:15.264 --> 00:59:17.389
One person can spoil the whole.

00:59:17.889 --> 00:59:22.222
Only people who want to be Gurus have to stay in the ashram.

00:59:22.264 --> 00:59:25.056
It's not going to be made a convenience for anyone.

00:59:27.222 --> 00:59:31.138
But the other way around is that,

00:59:31.139 --> 00:59:33.764
"We are going to look after ourselves,

00:59:33.806 --> 00:59:36.889
we have to become this, we have to grow,

00:59:36.931 --> 00:59:38.597
we have to do it."

00:59:44.138 --> 00:59:48.098
Then it's just, the other way round, everything works out,

00:59:48.138 --> 00:59:49.973
I don't have to tell you.

00:59:50.014 --> 00:59:52.347
You know this is so base and so gross

00:59:52.806 --> 00:59:54.722
that after being here for so many years,

00:59:55.472 --> 01:00:00.138
you should all have become avadhutas by now, absolutely.

01:00:00.138 --> 01:00:02.639
Controlling all elements, everything, should have been possible;

01:00:03.180 --> 01:00:05.889
but stilI you are under the grip of the elements,

01:00:06.389 --> 01:00:08.305
how can you control it ?

01:00:15.264 --> 01:00:20.098
First of all get out of the slavery, this mental slavery.

01:00:22.014 --> 01:00:26.514
"Alright if it is there, it is there, if it is not there it doesn't matter.

01:00:26.556 --> 01:00:28.389
Nothing is more important than me,

01:00:28.806 --> 01:00:30.514
I am the king of the whole world.

01:00:30.556 --> 01:00:32.681
If I have to sleep on the ground I can sleep,

01:00:32.681 --> 01:00:34.639
if I have to sleep in the palaces I can sleep,

01:00:34.639 --> 01:00:38.514
nothing can dominate me." Then you are the master.

01:00:40.472 --> 01:00:42.806
You know in India, there are some Sahaja Yogis

01:00:42.848 --> 01:00:48.389
who are controlling definitely controlling, elements.

01:00:48.931 --> 01:00:52.347
We have examples of that, lots of things have been published

01:00:52.389 --> 01:00:55.138
you know in Nirmala Yoga, you must have heard.

01:00:55.848 --> 01:00:58.139
But you meet them, you'll find they are avadhutas

01:00:58.180 --> 01:01:00.764
and when they talk you feel a great sage is talking,

01:01:00.806 --> 01:01:03.430
and the way they behave, all the time you see their behaviour

01:01:03.472 --> 01:01:05.056
and everything is so great.

01:01:05.098 --> 01:01:06.764
We need people of that calibre today,

01:01:06.806 --> 01:01:09.472
because that is the situation of all nations.

01:01:12.806 --> 01:01:17.098
You have to be extra-good, because today is not a time

01:01:17.138 --> 01:01:20.264
when we can allow things to go, as they are.

01:01:24.556 --> 01:01:27.098
Or we are not just disciples,

01:01:27.098 --> 01:01:28.973
we all have to become gurus.

01:01:32.014 --> 01:01:36.347
And it is not the time when you can play with time.

01:01:36.347 --> 01:01:42.430
You cannot play with evil. You have to surmount it.

01:01:42.472 --> 01:01:44.264
You have to come on top of it, it is the time

01:01:44.305 --> 01:01:47.014
when the whole ship is going to be drowned or saved.

01:01:47.056 --> 01:01:48.722
This is the situation today.

01:01:49.305 --> 01:01:52.430
And that's why you have got your realization from God.

01:01:53.139 --> 01:01:55.264
If that precarious time had not arrived,

01:01:55.305 --> 01:01:58.305
how many of you really think you deserved it?

01:01:59.014 --> 01:02:04.681
But you got it, because the time is such that everybody

01:02:04.681 --> 01:02:08.305
must be given realization, and they must be given all powers

01:02:08.347 --> 01:02:10.139
so that they come up.

01:02:10.180 --> 01:02:12.056
But if you do not open your heart,

01:02:12.098 --> 01:02:14.430
put all your attention to your Spirit,

01:02:14.430 --> 01:02:16.639
these powers will not work out.

01:02:16.681 --> 01:02:18.681
None of these powers will work out in you.

01:02:19.514 --> 01:02:21.806
This is the problem.

01:02:21.806 --> 01:02:24.931
Every Guru had a command on the elements.

01:02:25.472 --> 01:02:27.848
Nanaka, you know definitely.

01:02:28.305 --> 01:02:34.305
People were sitting there and they asked him for the water

01:02:34.764 --> 01:02:40.472
and he put his hand on a rock and the water started pouring down.

01:02:41.889 --> 01:02:45.138
That's why it is called Punjab, Punja :

01:02:45.806 --> 01:02:50.597
five; and the five rivers exist there, too.

01:02:54.556 --> 01:02:59.139
It is said about all of them that they had powers over the elements.

01:03:01.889 --> 01:03:04.098
So how much we are lacking ?

01:03:04.098 --> 01:03:09.514
Still we are like other people who are selling cheap things,

01:03:10.180 --> 01:03:18.514
or who are busy making cheap things, or who are of no value.

01:03:19.222 --> 01:03:21.764
You are the ones who have to save the whole world.

01:03:23.681 --> 01:03:27.514
And the maximum of my life, blood and toil and everything,

01:03:27.556 --> 01:03:29.889
sweat, I've put in this land of yours.

01:03:30.430 --> 01:03:32.556
And the time is coming for me to go.

01:03:33.056 --> 01:03:38.722
Only three years more are left; before that,

01:03:38.764 --> 01:03:41.138
I hope, we establish an ashram.

01:03:41.180 --> 01:03:42.764
We need not pay for it,

01:03:42.764 --> 01:03:47.014
but, you have to be ready to occupy it,

01:03:47.014 --> 01:03:49.056
otherwise you cannot occupy it I can tell you,

01:03:49.056 --> 01:03:51.389
you cannot get any more blessings of God.

01:03:52.180 --> 01:03:54.180
So why should God bless you ?

01:03:54.180 --> 01:03:56.056
This is the point one should ask oneself.

01:03:56.098 --> 01:04:01.639
Are you your own Spirit or you are all else but the Spirit!

01:04:03.806 --> 01:04:08.848
But when I say something, it just goes as a big roaring,

01:04:09.639 --> 01:04:12.973
I don't know if the frequency has reached your ears or not,

01:04:13.014 --> 01:04:15.889
but I would request you now,

01:04:15.931 --> 01:04:19.514
as Gavin has asked me for Guru Nanaka's day,

01:04:19.514 --> 01:04:21.138
I really didn't want to come.

01:04:21.138 --> 01:04:24.389
Because to talk of Guru Nanaka and to hear about him,

01:04:26.347 --> 01:04:29.138
one has to be a very great person.

01:04:33.305 --> 01:04:38.180
Because such a light to bear, you have to make up yourself.

01:04:38.222 --> 01:04:40.973
Everything else is important,

01:04:44.389 --> 01:04:49.305
then how can you talk of Sahaja Yoga coming there.

01:04:52.931 --> 01:04:54.973
I went to America, I was surprised!

01:04:54.973 --> 01:04:56.848
Americans whatever it is, few people,

01:04:56.848 --> 01:04:59.305
but to them Sahaja Yoga is the most important thing.

01:04:59.347 --> 01:05:01.973
They talk of nothing but Sahaja Yoga, their life is Sahaja Yoga,

01:05:02.014 --> 01:05:04.722
morning till evening they are working out Sahaja Yoga,

01:05:04.764 --> 01:05:07.722
nothing else, they are not bothered.

01:05:07.722 --> 01:05:09.556
Australians you know.

01:05:15.014 --> 01:05:23.180
But the Heart is not open, the Spirit has not shown its light.

01:05:23.848 --> 01:05:31.931
It is the one that gives you complete satisfaction, complete joy,

01:05:32.848 --> 01:05:37.014
complete Guru's principle, because then you start giving.

01:05:37.056 --> 01:05:39.430
If there is no light what are you giving? Darkness ?

01:05:41.722 --> 01:05:43.556
What are you giving to others ?

01:05:44.305 --> 01:05:48.347
The darkness that is within you, if you are going to give that....

01:05:51.722 --> 01:06:03.098
