01:12:29.722 --> 01:12:32.681
and the muscles so developed and the man,

01:12:32.722 --> 01:12:34.764
he stands up and the way he talks!

01:12:34.764 --> 01:12:36.848
And absolutely humble person.

01:12:43.139 --> 01:12:45.722
No wonder Christ chose fishermen.

01:12:46.764 --> 01:12:51.014
While he has got thousands of fishermen as his disciples,

01:12:51.514 --> 01:12:53.722
but he doesn't call them disciples,

01:12:53.764 --> 01:12:55.098
he says they are all Mother's children.

01:12:55.639 --> 01:12:57.472
Thousands! You don't know.

01:12:57.514 --> 01:12:59.556
He has been calling me to go to them,

01:12:59.556 --> 01:13:01.764
and all that but they come to my programme, some of them.

01:13:03.098 --> 01:13:06.180
And one day I have to go down, to those islands,

01:13:06.180 --> 01:13:08.681
any one of the islands he said you come they will be all there

01:13:08.681 --> 01:13:10.514
the whole day waiting for you.

01:13:10.556 --> 01:13:15.014
But the way he is there is surprising.

01:13:17.347 --> 01:13:21.098
When I am there he brings fishes for me.

01:13:21.138 --> 01:13:25.430
But I said, you see, I eat fishes that you bring

01:13:25.472 --> 01:13:27.681
but what about my other children.

01:13:27.722 --> 01:13:31.722
He said no, next time, all the fishes will be sent to you.

01:13:31.764 --> 01:13:33.931
And he sent one truck-load to me, you would not believe!

01:13:34.514 --> 01:13:37.597
I said now I don't even have truck-load of disciples,

01:13:37.597 --> 01:13:39.430
who is going to eat all this?

01:13:42.472 --> 01:13:45.347
And he said, "Nothing, I just went and told fishermen

01:13:45.347 --> 01:13:48.180
that Mother has asked for fishes and everybody gave their fishes.

01:13:48.430 --> 01:13:50.014
One day they will not have fishes,

01:13:50.056 --> 01:13:52.138
what is there, what does it matter."

01:13:52.138 --> 01:13:55.848
Imagine those people who live day-to-day in that country.

01:13:58.848 --> 01:14:03.180
Modi told the newspaper people

01:14:03.222 --> 01:14:05.514
that we can control the elements

01:14:05.556 --> 01:14:07.264
somehow by Mother's grace.

01:14:07.305 --> 01:14:11.138
So the newspaper people felt they were very much boasting.

01:14:11.138 --> 01:14:14.389
But it is true, they can.

01:14:16.389 --> 01:14:20.056
To them it is not boasting it is just what it is they are seeing.

01:14:20.056 --> 01:14:23.139
They are telling the truth, you see.

01:14:23.180 --> 01:14:24.639
But that should happen.

01:14:24.681 --> 01:14:26.347
We should also have some things

01:14:26.389 --> 01:14:28.222
to boast here. Important.

01:14:28.222 --> 01:14:32.931
So now we have the other phase as I told you,

01:14:32.973 --> 01:14:42.973
is of becoming the Guru of yourself.

01:14:43.556 --> 01:14:47.681
Detaching yourself, identifying yourself with the Spirit

01:14:47.722 --> 01:14:49.597
which is growing in its light.

01:14:51.764 --> 01:14:55.514
So detachment. One has to develop detachment.

01:14:56.098 --> 01:14:58.389
'My' mother, it starts like that;

01:14:58.430 --> 01:15:04.389
my mother is suffering from cancer, my father is suffering from madness,

01:15:05.014 --> 01:15:06.848
Mother can you cure them ?

01:15:09.430 --> 01:15:11.931
So now first I cure mother and father.

01:15:12.430 --> 01:15:15.222
Then I'm married, my wife is like this,

01:15:15.264 --> 01:15:24.138
my child is like this then my house, then my motorcar,

01:15:24.430 --> 01:15:27.597
then my dog, then my umbrella!

01:15:30.973 --> 01:15:37.806
I have to go suddenly from A to Z, from Z to A.

01:15:40.430 --> 01:15:51.973
Alright, I can do, up to a point, but for what? For what?

01:15:52.556 --> 01:15:56.472
Why to cure the mother, father, brother, sisters,

01:15:56.472 --> 01:16:01.597
every relationship, the 10th marriage and the 11th divorce ?

01:16:02.138 --> 01:16:05.138
Why to correct all this? For what?

01:16:08.681 --> 01:16:14.347
It must have some purpose, and if that purpose cannot be served,

01:16:14.931 --> 01:16:17.722
what is the use of doing it?

01:16:18.472 --> 01:16:24.597
The purpose is that you at least leave all these things in my hands

01:16:25.138 --> 01:16:26.931
and detach yourself.

01:16:26.973 --> 01:16:30.056
But you want to bring the case to Me as well as worry about it.

01:16:31.180 --> 01:16:33.389
Detachment.

01:16:35.931 --> 01:16:39.014
But the idea of detachment is this!

01:16:39.014 --> 01:16:42.514
"I'm very detached about money, Mother, absolutely.

01:16:42.556 --> 01:16:45.222
I'm not bothered. I keep the lights on,

01:16:45.264 --> 01:16:46.889
why to worry about money ?"

01:16:49.138 --> 01:16:50.931
This is the argument,

01:16:50.931 --> 01:16:55.139
"Why should we worry about looking after the gas and all that,

01:16:55.180 --> 01:16:59.973
after all we are detached people. We are in detachment, you see.

01:17:00.848 --> 01:17:02.681
We are not attached to money."

01:17:02.848 --> 01:17:04.514
But who is going to pay ?

01:17:06.764 --> 01:17:11.597
The other type of detachment that. I see, very interesting one is this one:

01:17:12.180 --> 01:17:18.264
"I'm very detached, so I'm not bothered about having a bath,

01:17:20.806 --> 01:17:22.514
having all kinds of diseases,

01:17:22.931 --> 01:17:25.556
having all kinds of problems within myself,

01:17:25.639 --> 01:17:28.222
giving my problems to others. I'm detached!

01:17:28.681 --> 01:17:32.347
Why should I cover myself ? I'm detached.

01:17:32.764 --> 01:17:35.014
If I get cold, I'm detached,

01:17:35.347 --> 01:17:37.347
let everybody get cold from me.

01:17:38.722 --> 01:17:40.764
What can I do, I'm detached.

01:17:41.305 --> 01:17:43.764
I've got cold, so what does it matter,

01:17:43.764 --> 01:17:45.264
I'm a detached personality.

01:17:45.347 --> 01:17:46.681
Why should others mind?

01:17:46.681 --> 01:17:48.556
They should also get detached."

01:17:54.222 --> 01:17:57.180
This is the ridiculous limit we can go

01:17:57.222 --> 01:18:03.305
in our idea of detachment! Detachment is from within.

01:18:03.305 --> 01:18:12.098
You are not bothered. You are not bothered.

01:18:12.098 --> 01:18:14.305
You know your Mother.

01:18:15.138 --> 01:18:18.931
The first detachment is shown in generosity.

01:18:19.848 --> 01:18:30.056
Detachment is generosity. Grezna is.

01:18:30.472 --> 01:18:33.556
She sold her ornaments for nothing at all.

01:18:33.597 --> 01:18:35.514
I mean I would never have accepted that money,

01:18:35.556 --> 01:18:38.514
but she just sold them. It's remarkable.

01:18:39.056 --> 01:18:46.305
She sold them She is Polish not English. She sold her ornaments ;

01:18:46.347 --> 01:18:48.514
and this is what communism has done to people.

01:18:48.681 --> 01:18:50.180
They are very detached,

01:18:50.222 --> 01:18:52.639
communists are very detached people I tell you.

01:18:55.556 --> 01:19:00.764
Of course I would never take that money, that's theirs,

01:19:00.806 --> 01:19:03.806
but the way she did it, just like that.

01:19:03.806 --> 01:19:09.973
For God's work alright what is ornaments, take it.

01:19:10.014 --> 01:19:14.931
I mean you know I've given away so many of my ornaments

01:19:14.973 --> 01:19:16.931
to keep relations alright.

01:19:19.556 --> 01:19:22.681
The other day I gave away my Kara to Christine,

01:19:22.681 --> 01:19:24.639
you know that when she got engaged.

01:19:24.639 --> 01:19:26.806
Just it came out of the hand and went away.

01:19:26.848 --> 01:19:32.180
I was detached you see, I never even felt the coming out !

01:19:33.722 --> 01:19:35.347
So much detached that Christine told me

01:19:35.389 --> 01:19:40.098
she was cramped up with pressure but to me it was just, just nothing.

01:19:40.889 --> 01:19:51.597
Dust. So that detachment has to come.

01:19:51.639 --> 01:19:56.180
Now you should know which part you are there.

01:19:56.180 --> 01:20:01.806
Like idea of detachment should not be

01:20:01.848 --> 01:20:06.681
that - I would say hippy style of detachment,

01:20:06.722 --> 01:20:08.889
that you have right to exploit everybody else.

01:20:10.848 --> 01:20:13.889
And the other type as I told you. which is very ridiculous.

01:20:14.389 --> 01:20:17.430
It's not an idea, it's a thing,

01:20:17.430 --> 01:20:21.347
it's your awareness itself which is detached.

01:20:28.222 --> 01:20:34.222
So, these four things for your material side is important.

01:20:36.347 --> 01:20:41.973
What you eat is not so important,

01:20:42.014 --> 01:20:43.389
because whatever you eat,

01:20:43.430 --> 01:20:45.806
if the brain is going to be such a non-sensical thing

01:20:45.848 --> 01:20:49.264
it's better whether you eat it or not, makes no difference does it?

01:20:49.305 --> 01:20:53.098
Analyze it, like in the hotel, what will you have,

01:20:53.098 --> 01:20:55.098
" I'll have pancakes," what will you have,

01:20:55.098 --> 01:20:57.222
" I'll have this I'll have that", for what ?

01:20:57.764 --> 01:20:59.973
I just don't understand why waste so much energy,

01:21:00.014 --> 01:21:02.639
why not you all have pancakes all of you put together.

01:21:03.889 --> 01:21:08.472
It's a very big thing you know. Or, today I'll have this.

01:21:08.472 --> 01:21:15.514
"I". Out of all this materialism what comes out is Mr "I".

01:21:17.639 --> 01:21:20.014
So we develop this Mr I.

01:21:20.639 --> 01:21:25.014
So the word "I" must go away, we should speak "we".

01:21:26.764 --> 01:21:32.264
"We" means you and all the Sahaja Yogis put together.

01:21:34.056 --> 01:21:38.014
When you say "we" you will find it will be different.

01:21:38.014 --> 01:21:41.430
Or take your name, like "this Norman."

01:21:42.472 --> 01:21:47.222
"This Norman won't listen," like children say.

01:21:47.264 --> 01:21:50.889
I asked a little boy, will you go home ? "

01:21:51.389 --> 01:21:58.597
I will go, but this (his name was Munna) this Munna, won't go,

01:21:58.639 --> 01:22:09.056
he's very obstinate, what can I do ?" This is detachment.

01:22:09.639 --> 01:22:12.098
To speak in third person is detachment,

01:22:12.098 --> 01:22:17.597
in which you are not in the picture...

01:22:17.639 --> 01:22:19.222
you are a witness.

01:22:19.264 --> 01:22:20.430
You are the witness in the show.

01:22:20.472 --> 01:22:24.264
So this detachment should work in such a way

01:22:24.305 --> 01:22:26.264
that you should witness the whole show,

01:22:26.264 --> 01:22:27.806
you're not involved into it.

01:22:27.848 --> 01:22:32.556
But just see what happens, in collectivity also.

01:22:34.138 --> 01:22:36.889
It becomes a political issue certainly,

01:22:36.931 --> 01:22:41.056
in Sahaja Yoga also, political issue; nothing short of political issue!

01:22:41.597 --> 01:22:48.430
We are not here fighting like union leaders.

01:22:49.139 --> 01:22:53.514
We are all leaders ! Where is the time to fight?

01:22:58.639 --> 01:23:02.098
Whom are we to fight , that we have to decide.

01:23:02.681 --> 01:23:06.514
So, as far as all these things concerned,

01:23:06.514 --> 01:23:10.639
are detachment and attachment to Spirit.

01:23:13.430 --> 01:23:15.180
So we go further,

01:23:15.222 --> 01:23:19.556
see now what should be our attitude on our mental level.

01:23:21.305 --> 01:23:27.098
Physically you have seen that you have to develop

01:23:27.098 --> 01:23:31.305
a complete detachment in these four ways that I have told you.

01:23:31.931 --> 01:23:35.556
Now on your mental level what you have to do,

01:23:36.305 --> 01:23:46.764
is to understand the essence of every writing,

01:23:47.264 --> 01:23:52.098
try to discriminate between Vidya and avidya.

01:23:52.264 --> 01:24:00.681
Because avidya will kill you, will take away your energy,

01:24:01.264 --> 01:24:04.305
but vidya will sustain.

01:24:04.889 --> 01:24:10.430
So try to find out books which are supporting vidya.

01:24:10.889 --> 01:24:13.848
I was surprised, there is a lady Barbara,

01:24:13.848 --> 01:24:15.889
she met only last time Gavin,

01:24:15.889 --> 01:24:19.514
and she has written such a tremendous book, you'd be amazed!

01:24:20.931 --> 01:24:24.681
I mean of such a level on Sahaja Yoga ! Very direct.

01:24:24.722 --> 01:24:29.222
I'll show you that, and you know that book is now being considered

01:24:29.264 --> 01:24:32.514
for giving her a.doctorate, can you believe it I

01:24:32.514 --> 01:24:34.430
In an American university;

01:24:34.472 --> 01:24:36.056
of course that's only possible in America.

01:24:36.098 --> 01:24:42.098
But still that book has that level,

01:24:42.098 --> 01:24:44.014
I was amazed at the book!

01:24:44.056 --> 01:24:50.597
So try to gather nourishment, like reading Devi Mahatmya,

01:24:50.639 --> 01:24:53.138
reading about, finding out about Bible

01:24:53.139 --> 01:24:57.389
and finding about other scriptures, about Koran - this that,

01:24:57.430 --> 01:25:00.848
and which supports you, which nourishes you.

01:25:02.264 --> 01:25:10.764
Blake, Kabir, Nanaka. I mean there are so many, Laotze.

01:25:11.639 --> 01:25:15.889
This is the good - is the knowledge. But you'll be amazed,

01:25:15.889 --> 01:25:18.430
once you start doing it, it comes to you.

01:25:18.430 --> 01:25:25.347
I met a man near Rahuri - as you know we go there,

01:25:28.138 --> 01:25:31.889
and there's a man who just drives a bullock cart,

01:25:32.681 --> 01:25:36.722
and he had brought the bullock cart to take me down

01:25:37.180 --> 01:25:39.848
to one of the programmes, you know what we do there.

01:25:39.848 --> 01:25:43.138
And he was sitting there, we were waiting, I was talking, to him.

01:25:43.138 --> 01:25:46.056
And I felt an Avadhuta is sitting there to drive me,

01:25:46.056 --> 01:25:49.639
I mean uneducated absolutely, he's never known books,

01:25:49.681 --> 01:25:52.180
he does not know how to write, but the way he was talking I said,

01:25:52.222 --> 01:25:55.305
"Oh God, from where this knowledge!

01:26:00.389 --> 01:26:03.098
From where was all this coming, this wisdom!

01:26:03.138 --> 01:26:04.848
Such wisdom, I tell you!''

01:26:05.514 --> 01:26:09.305
Such wisdom that I was just stunned, I was stunned really!

01:26:09.347 --> 01:26:13.597
From a man who is not even been to any school-college.

01:26:13.639 --> 01:26:15.931
Christ did not go to any school or college.

01:26:17.973 --> 01:26:20.014
Such wisdom, you can't imagine.

01:26:20.056 --> 01:26:22.180
You meet him next time when you go there.

01:26:22.806 --> 01:26:27.889
If somebody could translate him... you feel like touching his feet

01:26:27.889 --> 01:26:30.639
the way - extremely unassuming simple man,

01:26:30.639 --> 01:26:37.931
wearing a white, clean topi and clean dress and driving me down.

01:26:38.139 --> 01:26:41.597
And to him this was the greatest privilege of the whole world --

01:26:41.639 --> 01:26:44.931
is to drive me; he said "It must be the greatest of all --

01:26:44.973 --> 01:26:47.597
something I must have done - to be able to drive you."

01:26:48.139 --> 01:26:52.014
And in such simple ways he was explaining to me

01:26:52.014 --> 01:26:55.098
about the character of the bullocks and the human beings --

01:26:55.681 --> 01:26:59.681
just imagine! And the things he talked about,

01:26:59.722 --> 01:27:02.430
if I tell you, you won't believe - so I just don't know...

01:27:03.305 --> 01:27:09.681
That's the sign of a great man, he doesn't talk of frivolous things,

01:27:09.681 --> 01:27:11.764
he has no time to talk about frivolous things.

01:27:11.764 --> 01:27:13.347
I have seen my own grandchildren --

01:27:13.389 --> 01:27:15.514
they never talk of frivolous things, they have no time,

01:27:15.514 --> 01:27:17.056
they are busy, you know.

01:27:17.056 --> 01:27:19.639
All the time clearing out, when they came here, they said

01:27:19.639 --> 01:27:21.305
"We have to clear out this Brompton Square,

01:27:21.347 --> 01:27:23.430
then we have to clear out this Knights bridge,

01:27:23.430 --> 01:27:25.056
then we have to clear out this London,

01:27:25.098 --> 01:27:26.848
then we have to clear out this England.

01:27:26.889 --> 01:27:28.389
Where is the map of England, bring it,"

01:27:28.389 --> 01:27:31.014
all the time they were busy, you see, clearing out, and then,

01:27:31.056 --> 01:27:32.514
"this place is this, this place is this.

01:27:32.514 --> 01:27:34.347
Oh God this horrible,

01:27:34.347 --> 01:27:36.098
bring some shoes, do this do that,"

01:27:36.098 --> 01:27:38.639
all the time they were busy morning till evening.

01:27:38.681 --> 01:27:41.597
They would go upstairs in the room and they are busy.

01:27:41.639 --> 01:27:43.389
They are busy people, they have no time to talk

01:27:43.430 --> 01:27:44.973
of the mundane things and all that.

01:27:44.973 --> 01:27:47.098
Then I brought some dolls and toys, for them.

01:27:47.138 --> 01:27:51.180
They put all of them there and they put them, and the map there,

01:27:51.180 --> 01:27:55.138
"now see now, (to dolls) now you look after, alright ?"

01:27:55.180 --> 01:27:58.597
You know they're talking to dolls like that.

01:27:58.639 --> 01:28:00.556
Dolls are their disciples. Teaching the dolls,

01:28:00.597 --> 01:28:04.347
"you see, don't sit like this, you must sit properly, you don't know.

01:28:04.347 --> 01:28:05.931
You can't bend your knees ?

01:28:05.973 --> 01:28:07.973
Better learn that, you must learn to bend your knees,"

01:28:08.014 --> 01:28:10.597
because dolls have straight legs!

01:28:15.430 --> 01:28:18.681
And all the boys, even the little children,

01:28:18.722 --> 01:28:21.764
I have seen the way they are busy all the time doing Sahaja Yoga.

01:28:24.264 --> 01:28:28.305
Every level they are working.

01:28:29.556 --> 01:28:35.222
As today I was telling Rustom about my own father.

01:28:36.056 --> 01:28:38.014
You see, he was a learned man, of course.

01:28:38.014 --> 01:28:42.931
But when he talked, he used to talk of something,

01:28:42.931 --> 01:28:47.931
like I told him about the state of a person, called Sambhranta.

01:28:48.514 --> 01:28:53.014
He told me that, "Human beings are very different from God.

01:28:53.514 --> 01:28:57.180
When God incarnates then the Sambhranta state,

01:28:57.222 --> 01:28:59.973
which is awakening between the subconscious

01:29:00.014 --> 01:29:05.931
to the conscious state, is direct, you see.

01:29:05.931 --> 01:29:08.139
He comes down directly But human beings

01:29:08.180 --> 01:29:12.889
go this way, they never go straight.

01:29:13.389 --> 01:29:15.931
See God descends, so he descends properly,

01:29:15.973 --> 01:29:18.889
but ascent is always in a very separate way.

01:29:18.931 --> 01:29:21.556
It goes on like this, and he gathers everything

01:29:21.597 --> 01:29:25.347
that is in his subconscious, so the Sambhranta state,

01:29:25.389 --> 01:29:28.681
where he is waking up, is such a dangerous thing

01:29:28.681 --> 01:29:30.222
that he can gather up anything.

01:29:30.264 --> 01:29:33.889
And by the time he gathers up the dreams he becomes something so funny.

01:29:33.973 --> 01:29:38.848
He may look at God whom he has seen in his dream

01:29:38.889 --> 01:29:42.180
like a witch, and the witch like a bird."

01:29:42.806 --> 01:29:51.472
I saw him always busy. I mean to talk to him,

01:29:51.472 --> 01:29:55.722
I found a companion and he found me a companion sort of a thing.

01:29:55.764 --> 01:29:58.098
He could talk, because his attention was there.

01:29:58.098 --> 01:30:01.014
His attention was not how every body has made their hair,

01:30:01.014 --> 01:30:04.514
and how they are sitting down or what dresses they are making,

01:30:04.556 --> 01:30:06.681
or what do you have in this thing - nothing.

01:30:06.722 --> 01:30:12.514
His attention was on the Spirit, his own Spirit and Spirit of others.

01:30:12.556 --> 01:30:20.180
And he was so dynamic in his brain that he knew your dictionary

01:30:20.180 --> 01:30:21.430
by heart, I tell you.

01:30:21.430 --> 01:30:23.639
He never consulted dictionary all his life --

01:30:23.639 --> 01:30:27.639
neither Sanskrit nor English, and he was master of 14 languages.

01:30:27.639 --> 01:30:33.764
Can you imagine! How he must have managed!

01:30:33.806 --> 01:30:37.389
He used to play tennis very well, he used to swim for 3 miles every day.

01:30:37.389 --> 01:30:40.931
3 miles. He had muscles that he could just lift you up. Yes!

01:30:43.889 --> 01:30:48.430
Very healthy personality, healthy man.

01:30:48.472 --> 01:30:50.931
Very generous, very generous.

01:30:50.973 --> 01:30:53.389
Much more generous than me, so you can imagine.

01:30:53.430 --> 01:30:55.931
Very generous, to him nothing mattered,

01:30:55.973 --> 01:30:57.639
"alright you like it, take it".

01:30:57.639 --> 01:31:01.222
He'll starve himself but he'll be generous.

01:31:01.264 --> 01:31:05.139
And a man of principle.

01:31:05.180 --> 01:31:10.764
So we come to the second point which is actually

01:31:10.806 --> 01:31:13.556
we have started the fifth one - which is mentally

01:31:13.597 --> 01:31:18.222
you must only take to things which are nourishing.

01:31:22.347 --> 01:31:24.222
Through vibratory awareness you will know.

01:31:24.222 --> 01:31:28.430
Ask other Sahaja Yogis, if you do not know.

01:31:28.848 --> 01:31:31.430
But take nourishing things to read and not horrible,

01:31:31.472 --> 01:31:33.722
detrimental to your growth.

01:31:33.764 --> 01:31:36.305
If you read them, you are responsible:

01:31:36.347 --> 01:31:41.180
You are real great readers I must say --

01:31:41.222 --> 01:31:43.514
you ask any name, everyone knows.

01:31:43.556 --> 01:31:45.347
I said who was Gropius, everyone knows.

01:31:45.389 --> 01:31:47.222
You need not be an academician to tell.

01:31:47.222 --> 01:31:50.889
Everyone knows, what happened, who is this, who is that.

01:31:50.889 --> 01:31:53.973
Out of your seeking you have done one good thing --

01:31:54.014 --> 01:31:56.430
to have read everything whether good or bad,

01:31:56.430 --> 01:31:58.305
whatever it is.

01:31:58.347 --> 01:32:00.639
But now after realisation, you must try to find out

01:32:00.639 --> 01:32:03.138
what you have to read, what you have to know,

01:32:03.138 --> 01:32:04.889
it should be nourishing.

01:32:04.889 --> 01:32:08.848
Talk that is nourishing, helpful.

01:32:08.889 --> 01:32:14.472
So in talk you should have compassion.

01:32:14.472 --> 01:32:19.222
If you are talking to someone you should be full of compassion.

01:32:19.264 --> 01:32:21.430
Sahaja Yoga is a system of compassion.

01:32:21.430 --> 01:32:26.098
A Guru has to be very-very patient.

01:32:26.138 --> 01:32:29.347
It is not like other Gurudom,

01:32:29.764 --> 01:32:32.597
or even real Gurus had no patience.

01:32:33.472 --> 01:32:38.806
This is a system where patience is the only way it will work out,

01:32:38.848 --> 01:32:41.014
because no Gurus gave realisation, it is only you

01:32:41.014 --> 01:32:43.472
who have to give it. And you know what is realisation.

01:32:43.514 --> 01:32:48.138
The other day we met one; the fellow sitting tight.

01:32:48.139 --> 01:32:56.056
They said, "We have failed Mother, we can't give him realisation,

01:32:56.098 --> 01:32:57.806
it's a hopeless case". I said, "Really ?"

01:32:57.806 --> 01:33:00.889
So I went there - at the end of it you see, they said,

01:33:00.931 --> 01:33:02.347
"Mother there's one fellow sitting".

01:33:02.389 --> 01:33:05.430
I wanted to aviod, you see, but they said.

01:33:05.472 --> 01:33:11.722
Alright, so raised his Kundalini, raised it up, tied it up,

01:33:11.764 --> 01:33:16.931
my hands bearing now. "Oh no, I didn't feel anything".

01:33:16.973 --> 01:33:23.931
I said, this fellow is least bothered

01:33:23.973 --> 01:33:26.138
how much we are working on him!

01:33:26.139 --> 01:33:28.138
He's just thinking he's obliging us."

01:33:28.138 --> 01:33:31.556
So then two or three people came forward, brought a light,

01:33:31.556 --> 01:33:35.014
put the light before him, did bandhan here and everything:

01:33:35.056 --> 01:33:38.973
Again I raised his Kundalini thrice:

01:33:39.014 --> 01:33:44.889
"No, not at all... ! "it went on like that for half an hour,

01:33:44.889 --> 01:33:46.222
then I gave up. I said,

01:33:46.264 --> 01:33:48.014
"Sir, I'm sorry, you are too great

01:33:48.014 --> 01:33:52.347
for realisation! We'll try again".

01:33:52.347 --> 01:33:58.639
"I'm not convinced..." And I was fagged out,

01:33:58.681 --> 01:34:02.139
I said "Really, I am convinced about you,

01:34:02.180 --> 01:34:04.764
so, you allow us to go", and then I came out.

01:34:04.806 --> 01:34:07.889
You have to have 'tremendous' patience and sense of humour --

01:34:07.931 --> 01:34:09.806
you just can't tell him off.

01:34:09.848 --> 01:34:12.222
You see if I told him ''You are good for nothing, useless,

01:34:12.222 --> 01:34:16.806
you have a bad Kundalini you go away from here get away, get lost."

01:34:16.806 --> 01:34:23.556
I couldn't say these things to him, I had to bear him through and not only,

01:34:23.556 --> 01:34:26.764
in the end I had to say you are a great man, you see.

01:34:26.806 --> 01:34:29.889
Because otherwise he would have used some other method.

01:34:29.889 --> 01:34:32.597
Because, already the ego was so big

01:34:32.597 --> 01:34:35.889
that with all the pins I put inside it, it could not deflate,

01:34:35.889 --> 01:34:38.722
it was made of a special fibre I think !

01:34:42.639 --> 01:34:45.014
It was such a difficult task.

01:34:45.056 --> 01:34:48.347
So one has to know that we have to be compassionate.

01:34:48.389 --> 01:34:53.014
We have to read something that nourishes our compassion.

01:34:53.056 --> 01:34:58.138
Read of people who gave away everything that they had.

01:34:58.139 --> 01:35:04.597
Tukarama. Read Tukarama. Tukarama was a poor man.

01:35:04.639 --> 01:35:09.389
And one day he went to some place and did some good job,

01:35:09.430 --> 01:35:14.973
so they gave him lots of sugar cane.

01:35:15.347 --> 01:35:17.889
His children were very fond of sugar cane.

01:35:18.931 --> 01:35:21.931
So on the way every child would ask, "give me one sugar cane".

01:35:21.973 --> 01:35:23.389
He was giving to everyone.

01:35:23.389 --> 01:35:25.180
When he came home only one was left.

01:35:25.222 --> 01:35:27.722
So the children said, "we are three".

01:35:27.722 --> 01:35:31.014
He said, "It's alright; next time I will bring for you,

01:35:31.056 --> 01:35:34.889
share it among you three". And they had it,

01:35:34.931 --> 01:35:37.764
they said, "better have it, now one more child will come

01:35:37.764 --> 01:35:39.389
and this will also go away".

01:35:41.931 --> 01:35:45.806
So one has to know about lives who have been giving.

01:35:47.264 --> 01:35:50.347
Read about people who have been giving.

01:35:51.014 --> 01:35:57.056
They gave their lives. They crucified them, they tortured them.

01:35:57.098 --> 01:35:59.264
They allowed to be exploited.

01:35:59.305 --> 01:36:01.347
They allowed to be poisoned.

01:36:01.347 --> 01:36:05.514
Head of such sacrifice, of great sacrifices.

01:36:05.556 --> 01:36:08.722
We are lucky people that we have seen all those things

01:36:08.764 --> 01:36:10.264
with our own eyes.

01:36:10.264 --> 01:36:13.722
But at least you be one of them, that you can at least,

01:36:13.764 --> 01:36:19.264
if not see, visualise it. You can. Bring that as your principle.

01:36:19.305 --> 01:36:25.556
So we move now, from detachment,

01:36:25.597 --> 01:36:29.472
which I've told you four types of detachment,

01:36:29.514 --> 01:36:35.389
and then I told you the nourishment of your mind

01:36:36.138 --> 01:36:38.848
and nourishment to your heart.

01:36:39.305 --> 01:36:46.014
Nothing nourishes more to a person than giving away.

01:36:46.514 --> 01:36:51.389
Nothing nourishes your heart, your compassion,

01:36:51.430 --> 01:36:53.597
unless and until you learn to give away.

01:36:53.764 --> 01:36:56.014
Now will you please make a list of things,

01:36:56.014 --> 01:37:02.056
"how many things you have given away in this one year, last one year".

01:37:02.098 --> 01:37:03.806
I can't because it is too much.

01:37:06.556 --> 01:37:10.639
Please make a list of things, "how many things",

01:37:10.681 --> 01:37:15.056
except for your brains you have given away to others

01:37:15.681 --> 01:37:21.472
without thinking about it, or have thought of giving.

01:37:25.639 --> 01:37:29.597
Since Christmas let us say, to this Christmas.

01:37:34.806 --> 01:37:42.806
Heart is opening. Think of giving.

01:37:44.264 --> 01:37:50.430
On material level, other help is there to give.

01:37:50.472 --> 01:37:55.514
But no, we don't even give the other help,

01:37:55.931 --> 01:37:58.389
for which you don't have to spend any money.

01:37:58.430 --> 01:38:00.056
Just give a hand.

01:38:00.722 --> 01:38:04.848
I have seen, very easy to make out,

01:38:05.430 --> 01:38:07.597
labour saving devices.

01:38:09.639 --> 01:38:13.681
Now, I have come here, some will be running,

01:38:13.722 --> 01:38:15.556
others are just sitting.

01:38:15.556 --> 01:38:19.138
Tea is brought to them, food is brought of them everything is done.

01:38:19.139 --> 01:38:22.556
They'll just put the plate also before: go and wash.

01:38:28.639 --> 01:38:35.138
Its not only selfishness but it is unmannerly, unmannerly to be like this.

01:38:38.973 --> 01:38:45.347
In Sahaja Yoga you have to be

01:38:45.347 --> 01:38:50.139
extremely busy helping others,

01:38:50.931 --> 01:38:54.180
at every point. To be helpful.

01:38:55.138 --> 01:38:58.764
You know Ravi Shankar's Guru was a very great,

01:38:59.764 --> 01:39:04.806
a very great man, a realized soul. He was a great person.

01:39:04.806 --> 01:39:06.305
So he knew so many things.

01:39:06.889 --> 01:39:12.139
And one day I was there, in the night you see, there was a doctor,

01:39:12.180 --> 01:39:16.806
we were his guests in a way, for dinner we had gone there.

01:39:17.138 --> 01:39:18.848
In the night the call came that,

01:39:18.889 --> 01:39:21.138
"I need you very much" to the doctor.

01:39:21.138 --> 01:39:22.639
The doctor said, "Now I'm tired".

01:39:22.639 --> 01:39:24.973
He was another very giving person, no doubt.

01:39:24.973 --> 01:39:27.222
He said, "Oh you must come, I have a big problem.

01:39:27.222 --> 01:39:31.056
See I saw a little baby."

01:39:31.098 --> 01:39:33.764
He said, "What baby have you found ?"

01:39:33.806 --> 01:39:36.056
He said, "its a baby," he was an old man,

01:39:36.098 --> 01:39:41.722
he said, "I found a baby of a deer which is suffering now,

01:39:41.722 --> 01:39:45.098
and the mother is dead and nobody is to look after it."

01:39:45.098 --> 01:39:49.139
So I said "Alright I'll also come with you",

01:39:49.180 --> 01:39:52.472
because I knew I will touch the baby. I went with him.

01:39:52.514 --> 01:40:00.305
So, he was sitting with the little thing near his heart.

01:40:00.347 --> 01:40:03.389
So the doctor said, "What are you doing ?"

01:40:03.430 --> 01:40:07.014
He said, "I'm trying to give him my life if possible,

01:40:07.014 --> 01:40:10.556
so that when you come at least you find him alive".

01:40:10.597 --> 01:40:12.931
Just like this, just love.

01:40:12.931 --> 01:40:18.222
So he took out the thing - doctor - his coat and all that,

01:40:18.264 --> 01:40:20.264
and he said, "alright put it down".

01:40:20.305 --> 01:40:22.472
He put it down very cautiously.

01:40:22.514 --> 01:40:24.222
I mean he was a realized soul, no doubt.

01:40:24.222 --> 01:40:28.305
I put my hand on the thing and it came to life,

01:40:28.347 --> 01:40:30.931
and it started, alright, he was very happy.

01:40:30.973 --> 01:40:35.472
He said, "You are a Devi, you are a Goddess, I can tell you.

01:40:35.514 --> 01:40:37.556
But one bad thing you have done." I said "What ? "

01:40:37.597 --> 01:40:41.098
You are married." I said, "But Devis must marry, also."

01:40:41.138 --> 01:40:44.014
He said, "No, supposing you have married a miserly man,

01:40:44.014 --> 01:40:45.556
then what will happen to you ?"

01:40:45.597 --> 01:40:48.347
I said, "I will see to it that, I don't marry a miserly man.

01:40:50.389 --> 01:40:53.514
That would be the greatest curse."

01:40:53.556 --> 01:40:56.056
He said, "I had the same type of a wife who was miserly,

01:40:56.098 --> 01:40:58.764
and I got fed up with her for her miserliness."

01:40:59.722 --> 01:41:03.264
So that is what it is : miserliness should be hated,

01:41:03.305 --> 01:41:09.806
absolutely to be hated, absolutely to be the worst of all.

01:41:09.806 --> 01:41:13.264
It's like leprosy for Sahaja Yogis. Miserliness.

01:41:13.264 --> 01:41:15.514
It's saving saving pounds, you know.

01:41:18.430 --> 01:41:20.848
That must go away from your mind,

01:41:23.180 --> 01:41:28.764
Miserliness to yourself is good, miserliness to others is bad.

01:41:28.806 --> 01:41:31.264
Gregoire told me a shocking thing.

01:41:31.305 --> 01:41:33.138
He said, "this is our culture."

01:41:33.139 --> 01:41:35.138
I said "Your culture ! what is it ?"

01:41:35.597 --> 01:41:39.222
You see, he said that "if we go in a hotel, and if somebody is paying,

01:41:39.264 --> 01:41:41.014
we start looking this side and that."

01:41:41.056 --> 01:41:43.931
I said, "Really !". He said, that is very common.

01:41:49.514 --> 01:41:51.681
I just cannot believe it ! This is culture!

01:41:51.722 --> 01:41:54.722
It is the opposite of culture. Whatever you may call it,

01:41:54.764 --> 01:41:58.139
it's not culture at all. Culture would be to come forward,

01:41:58.180 --> 01:42:01.931
"Alright I'll pay". But Americans are even worse, they'll say,

01:42:01.973 --> 01:42:04.597
"I paid for you yesterday, you pay today for me."

01:42:06.848 --> 01:42:10.222
It's absolutely disgraceful miserliness.

01:42:10.973 --> 01:42:14.472
But this is gracious; you see when somebody is paying,

01:42:14.472 --> 01:42:17.264
you look on the other side. It may be gracious, I don't know,

01:42:18.681 --> 01:42:23.180
whatever it is, it's just the same ; filth I tell you.

01:42:23.222 --> 01:42:26.389
So compassion ; compassion at any point.

01:42:26.389 --> 01:42:28.806
You may have to work till 2 o'clock, you may .

01:42:28.848 --> 01:42:30.722
have to work at 4 o'clock, doesn't matter.

01:42:30.764 --> 01:42:32.806
You have to work, you have to work, you have to work;

01:42:32.848 --> 01:42:36.098
because compassion itself is joy giving,

01:42:36.098 --> 01:42:41.222
because your Spirit is the Ocean of Compassion.

01:42:41.222 --> 01:42:47.848
There is no other way, there is no other way

01:42:47.848 --> 01:42:52.138
to enjoy your Spirit but to Give, to Give, to Give.

01:42:52.139 --> 01:42:54.681
Doesn't matter if you have not eaten your food, doesn't matter.

01:42:54.722 --> 01:42:58.056
Nothing matters.

01:42:59.556 --> 01:43:05.098
Many a times a you know that I don't have food for 24 hours sometimes,

01:43:05.138 --> 01:43:06.889
still I am giving.

01:43:06.931 --> 01:43:09.681
Its not necessary for this body to eat,

01:43:09.722 --> 01:43:14.222
the food of this body is compassion. That nourishes.

01:43:16.472 --> 01:43:19.347
So you have to be miserly towards yourself,

01:43:19.389 --> 01:43:21.222
but you must have compassion.

01:43:22.764 --> 01:43:25.389
Heart, open your heart.

01:43:26.138 --> 01:43:30.681
Open your heart first of all, for thankfulness.

01:43:34.806 --> 01:43:38.597
This is the other quality one should have.

